rows.label: qst002101_msg001
rows.name: 依頼

rows.label: qst002101_msg002
rows.name: 早く持ってきてほしいも

rows.label: qst002101_msg003
rows.name: どうもありがとう

rows.label: qst002101_msg0001
rows.name:
Ayup, Rex. You're a Driver now, are
ya, lad?

rows.label: qst002101_msg0002
rows.name:
Yeah. I'm still keeping up with the
salvaging though.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0003
rows.name:
Good job, because there was something
I wanted to ask you about...

rows.label: qst002101_msg0004
rows.name:
Ah, it's nowt major. I just thought I'd
see if a Driver could help.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0005
rows.name: Have you got a minute to hear me out?

rows.label: qst002101_msg0006
rows.name:
This watering hole's not been giving
out much water lately.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0007
rows.name:
So we're a bit short of water.
I can't have my bath, or get
my taters washed.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0008
rows.name:
It's not the only water supply we've
got, but I'm worried the other sources
might go the same way...

rows.label: qst002101_msg0009
rows.name: エネミー名（仮）が原因なんだよ

rows.label: qst002101_msg0010
rows.name:
I dunno if it's their mating season or
something, but they've built a load of
nests on the underside of the Divine Beast.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0011
rows.name:
It happened before, two years ago.
It's almost as bad as it was before.
We've let it build up, unfortunately.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0012
rows.name:
We had to call in a Driver just to come
and sort it out last time. Cost a fortune!

rows.label: qst002101_msg0013
rows.name:
I heard you were round Correl's
house, so I thought I'd ask you and
see if you could take care of it.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0014
rows.name: Cheers for that.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0015
rows.name:
これからエネミー（仮）用の
シリンダを渡すよ

rows.label: qst002101_msg0016
rows.name:
You should use one of them. You can
salvage some from Messet Point.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0017
rows.name:
そうすれば
巨神獣に巣くってるエネミー（仮）が
引っかかるはずだ

rows.label: qst002101_msg0018
rows.name: There might be two or three of them.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0019
rows.name:
Not a right lot, but mind you don't
get hurt.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0101
rows.name:
Messet Pointから
エネミー（仮）用シリンダーを使って
サルベージしてくれ

rows.label: qst002101_msg0201
rows.name:
Thanks for that, lad! We've got water
coming out again now.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0202
rows.name:
I can have me bath now, and get me
spuds polished.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0203
rows.name:
Aye, it's pretty handy having a local
lad become a Driver.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0204
rows.name:
You can take care of stuff that's
difficult for us lot in no time at all.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0205
rows.name:
And you're still keeping your hand in
with the salvaging too.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0206
rows.name: I'm impressed, lad!

rows.label: qst002101_msg0207
rows.name:
Well, here's the fee. I got everyone to
chip in for it.

rows.label: qst002101_msg0208
rows.name: You've earned it, lad!
